<hr id="read-marker"> To be added <hr id="read-marker">
  
United Left Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span> + <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>[? if sapd_formed:&nbsp;+ <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span>?]): [+ left_coalition_meck_stre +]%
  
Social-Liberal Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span>?][? if not lvp_formed: + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>?]): [+ social_liberal_coalition_meck_stre +]%

Bourgeois Coalition ([? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span>?] + <span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**DNVP**</span> + <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span> + <span style="color: #AFAFAF;">**Others**</span> + [? if kvp_formed: + <span style="color: #0087DC;">KVP</span> ?] + <span style="color: #3E88B3;">DNVP</span>): [+ true_bourgeois_coalition_meck_stre +]%

Right-Wing Coalition (<span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**DNVP**</span> + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span> + <span style="color: #3D3D3D;">**DVFP**</span> + <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>): [+ right_coalition_meck_stre +]%

@meck_stre_coalition_menu

- @social_liberal_coalition_meck_stre
- @bourgeois_coalition_meck_stre
- @left_coalition_meck_stre
- @spd_majority_meck_stre
- @right_wing_coalition_meck_stre
- @no_coalition_meck_stre
- @meck_stre_coalition_creator_option

@social_liberal_coalition_meck_stre
title: A Social-Liberal Coalition will be formed
choose-if: social_liberal_coalition_meck_stre >= 50 and dvp_relation >= 30
on-arrival: meck_stre_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; dvp_relation += 2; ddp_relation += 3; meck_stre_gov = "Social-Liberal"

@bourgeois_coalition_meck_stre
title: A bourgeois coalition is formed.
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">DDP</span> will cooperate with the <span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">DNVP</span>...
choose-if: true_bourgeois_coalition_meck_stre >= 50
view-if: social_liberal_coalition_meck_stre < 50 or dvp_relation < 30
on-arrival: meck_stre_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; meck_stre_gov = "Right"

You can't even rely on the <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">DDP</span>...

@left_coalition_meck_stre
title: A Coalition of the Left will be formed
subtitle: We will work alongside the KPD
choose-if: left_coalition_meck_stre >= 50 and kpd_relation >= 50
on-arrival: meck_stre_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; workers_kpd += 2; workers_dvp -= 2; workers_dnvp -= 1; rural_spd += 1; meck_stre_gov = "Left"

@spd_majority_meck_stre
title: We don't need any coalition partners
view-if: spd_r_meck_stre >= 50
on-arrival: meck_stre_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; workers_spd += 1; workers_dnvp -= 2; rural_spd += 1; rural_dnvp -= 1; meck_stre_gov = "SPD"

@right_wing_coalition_meck_stre
title: The Right forms a government.
choose-if: right_coalition_meck_stre >= 50
view-if: right_coalition_meck_stre >= 50
on-arrival: meck_stre_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; rural_nsdap += 1; dvp_relation -= 3; meck_stre_gov = "Far-Right"

This can't end well...

@no_coalition_meck_stre
title: There is no possible government arrangement
subtitle: New elections will be called...
on-arrival: meck_stre_election_2_trigger_time = time + 3; new_middle_dnvp += 1
view-if: social_liberal_coalition_meck_stre < 50 and right_coalition_meck_stre < 50 and right_coalition_meck_stre < 50


@meck_stre_coalition_creator_option
title: Custom Coalition Creator (Test)
subtitle: Dear Test Players, if you see this, please tell me what you think
on-arrival: meck_stre_coalition_r = spd_r_meck_stre; meck_stre_spd = "government"
go-to: meck_stre_coalition_creator

@meck_stre_coalition_creator
title: Coalition Creator

Current support: [+ meck_stre_coalition_r +]%

- @meck_stre_invite_kpd: Invite the <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_sapd: Invite the <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_uspd: Invite the <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_ddp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**DDP**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_lvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_hb: Invite the <span style="color: #CEDD8A;">Home Owners</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_others: Invite the <span style="color: [+ i_colour +];">**Others**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_dvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_kvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ kvp_colour +];">**KVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_wp: Invite the <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>
- @meck_stre_invite_dnvp: Invite the <span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**DNVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_check_out: Check out.
- @meck_stre_drop_kpd: Drop the <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_sapd: Drop the <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_uspd: Drop the <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_ddp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**DDP**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_lvp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_hb: Drop the <span style="color: #CEDD8A;">Home Owners</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_others: Drop the <span style="color: [+ other_colour +];">**Others**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_dvp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_kvp: Drop the <span style="color: [+ kvp_colour +];">**KVP**</span>
- @meck_stre_drop_wp: Drop the <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>
- @return_to_meck_stre: Return


@meck_stre_invite_kpd
view-if: kpd_r_meck_stre > 0 and not meck_stre_kpd = "government"
choose-if: kpd_relation >= 50 and meck_stre_dvp == "opposition" and meck_stre_wp == "opposition" and (not meck_stre_z == "government" or z_leader == "Joos" or z_leader == "Kaiser")
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span> will demand radical policies.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if  kpd_relation < 50: We need better relations. ?][? if not meck_stre_dvp == "opposition": They are not really pleased about our partners. ?]
on-arrival: meck_stre_coalition_r = meck_stre_coalition_r + kpd_r_meck_stre; meck_stre_kpd = "government"
go-to: meck_stre_coalition_creator

@meck_stre_invite_sapd
view-if: sapd_r_meck_stre > 0 and not meck_stre_sapd = "government"
choose-if: sapd_relation >= 50 and meck_stre_dvp == "opposition" and meck_stre_wp == "opposition" and (not meck_stre_z == "government" or z_leader == "Joos" or z_leader == "Kaiser")
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ sapd_colour +];">**SAPD**</span> will demand radical policies.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if  sapd_relation < 50: We need better relations. ?][? if not meck_stre_dvp == "opposition": They are not really pleased about our partners. ?]
on-arrival: meck_stre_coalition_r = meck_stre_coalition_r + sapd_r_meck_stre; meck_stre_sapd = "government"
go-to: meck_stre_coalition_creator

@meck_stre_invite_uspd
view-if: uspd_r_meck_stre > 0 and not meck_stre_uspd = "government"
choose-if: uspd_relation >= 40 and meck_stre_wp == "opposition" and (not meck_stre_z == "government" or z_leader == "Joos" or z_leader == "Kaiser" or uspd_ideology == "Orthodox Marxism")
subtitle: [? if not uspd_ideology == "Orthodox Marxism": The <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span> will demand radical policies. ?][? if uspd_ideology == "Orthodox Marxism": Center Marxists are flexible. ?]
on-arrival: meck_stre_coalition_r = meck_stre_coalition_r + uspd_r_meck_stre; meck_stre_uspd = "government"
go-to: meck_stre_coalition_creator

@meck_stre_invite_ddp
view-if: ddp_r_meck_stre > 0 and not meck_stre_ddp = "government"
choose-if: ddp_relation >= 30 and (not meck_stre_kpd == "government" or kpd_leader == "Conciliators")
subtitle: [? if ddp_relation >= 65: The <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**DDP**</span> loves you! ?]
on-arrival: meck_stre_coalition_r = meck_stre_coalition_r + ddp_r_meck_stre; meck_stre_ddp = "government"
go-to: meck_stre_coalition_creator

@meck_stre_invite_lvp
view-if: lvp_r_meck_stre > 0 and not meck_stre_lvp = "government"
choose-if: lvp_relation >= 35 and (not meck_stre_kpd == "government" or kpd_leader == "Conciliators")
subtitle: [? if lvp_relation >= 75: The <span style="color: [+ lvp_colour +];">**LVP**</span> loves you! ?]
on-arrival: meck_stre_coalition_r = meck_stre_coalition_r + lvp_r_meck_stre; meck_stre_lvp = "government"
go-to: meck_stre_coalition_creator

@meck_stre_invite_dvp
view-if: dvp_r_meck_stre > 0 and not meck_stre_dvp = "government"
choose-if: dvp_relation >= 35 and meck_stre_kpd == "opposition" and meck_stre_sapd == "opposition"
subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span> demands tax cuts.
